workflows.name: Functional tests
workflows.display_title: VPN-82: Build Qt6 and client for apple universal binaries. (#5828)

head_commit.message:
VPN-82: Build Qt6 and client for apple universal binaries. (#5828)

* Build Qt6 for apple universal binaries
* Add MacOS universal builds in Taskcluster
* Limit golang libs to archs specified by CMAKE_OSX_ARCHITECTURES
* Rip out Sentry secrets for testing universal builds
* Install golang and sentry-cli via a fetch task
